": \"at least three locations\", \"from\": 2292, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"fire\", \"from\": 2333, \"to\": 2337}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The cables were connected to signal boxes and other rail infrastructure, he said.\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The cables\", \"from\": 2340, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"boxes\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"other rail infrastructure\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Preliminary information from French law enforcement and intelligence organizations indicates that anarchists or extreme leftist groups are likely responsible for the coordinated sabotage attack on the French high-speed rail network, two senior law enforcement and intelligence officials in the U.S. briefed on the matter said.\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2749, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2624, \"end\": 2630, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999048282052, \"rank\": 9.515289301093857e-08, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Preliminary information\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"French law enforcement\", \"from\": 2452, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"intelligence organizations\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"anarchists\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2531}, {\"ngram\": \"extreme leftist groups\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2557}, {\"ngram\": \"the coordinated sabotage attack\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2616}, {\"ngram\": \"two senior law enforcement\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\": \"intelligence officials\", \"from\": 2687, \"to\": 2709}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2721}, {\"ngram\": \"the matter\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The officials stressed the investigation is ongoing and the initial assessment is preliminary.\", \"fro