 \"a fine\", \"from\": 3244, \"to\": 3250}, {\"ngram\": \"225,000 euros\", \"from\": 3254, \"to\": 3267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French Transport Minister Patrice Vergriete also took to X, where he said \\\"coordinated malicious acts\\\" targeted several lines and would \\\"seriously disrupt traffic until this weekend.\\\"\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3290, \"end\": 3296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999048282052, \"rank\": 9.515289301093857e-08, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"X\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"coordinated malicious acts\", \"from\": 3364, \"to\": 3391}, {\"ngram\": \"several lines\", \"from\": 3402, \"to\": 3415}, {\"ngram\": \"traffic\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3452}, {\"ngram\": \"this weekend\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3471}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In comments aired by the French broadcaster BFMTV, Vergriete later said the disruptions appeared to unfold simultaneously and appeared intentional.\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3622, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3500, \"end\": 3506, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999048282052, \"rank\": 9.515289301093857e-08, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3519, \"end\": 3524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BFMTV\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BFM_TV\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 3478, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"Vergriete\", \"from\": 3526, \"to\": 3535}, {\"ngram\": \"the disruptions\", \"from\": 3547, \"to\": 3562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was unclear who might be responsible.\", \"from\": 3623, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One passenger, Ma\\u00ebliss Davy, 23, said she had planned to travel from Paris to Nantes, a city in the Upper Brittany region of western France, for a friend's birthday Saturday, but was surprised to receive a message on the SNCF app saying her train had been delayed due to an \\\"act of vandalism.\\\"\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3734, \"end\": 3739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5940602338297144e-21, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3743, \"end\": 3749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nantes_station\", \"score\": 0.8062195385563762, \"rank\": 0.24035694023318385, \"text\": \"Nantes\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nantes_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nantes_station\"}, {\"begin\": 3765, \"end\": 3779, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upper_Brittany\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Upper Brittany\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upper_Brittany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Upper_Brittany\"}, {\"begin\": 3798, \"end\": 3804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.325971297677575e-12, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3886, \"end\": 3890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SNCF\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SNCF\"}], \"noun_